---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/Page.astro';
import Callout from '@/components/Callout.astro';
import Appearances from '@/components/sections/Appearances.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Speaking">
	<p class="py-5 text-xl">
		As a speaker and event facilitator, I bring technical insights and engaging conversations to conferences, meetups,
		podcasts, and industry events. My experience spans technical presentations, panel moderation, and event hosting,
		creating memorable experiences for audiences across various formats.
	</p>

	<Appearances limit={9} />

	<div class="mb-8 mt-16 flex justify-center">
		<Callout title="Fun fact" variant="info">
			<p>
				Beyond tech conferences, I've had the honor of officiating <span class="font-bold">10 weddings</span>, bringing
				the same dedication to creating meaningful moments in people's lives.
			</p>
		</Callout>
	</div>

	<div class="pt-8">
		<h3>Want me at your event?</h3>

		<p>
			I'm always interested in new speaking opportunities. Whether it's a conference talk, panel moderation, or event
			hosting, let's discuss how I can contribute to making your event successful.
		</p>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
